Socket
Gateway


Ports:
    FTP         - 20 - Data, 21 - Control
    SSH         - 22
    TELNET      - 23
    SMTP        - 25
    DNS         - 53
    DHCP        - 67, 68
    HTTP        - 80
    POP3        - 110
    NTP         - 123
    IMAP        - 143
    BGP         - 179
    IMAP        - 143
    HTTPS/SSL   - 443
    UDP         - 1900
    RDP         - 3389
